      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>BLUE LOVE</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Sometimes I think Love is amazing</l>
          <l>Almost as painful as it's crazy</l>
          <l>Making us mad 'cause we’re feeling</l>
          <l>Believing, deceiving, giving</l>
          <l>Not receiving.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>It’s so insane,</l>
          <l>You try again to beat it,</l>
          <l>Cheat it and defeat it</l>
          <l>Then it kicks you</l>
          <l>Crazy it leaves you</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Sometimes I find</l>
          <l>That love is not always blind</l>
          <l>It takes you right from behind</l>
          <l>And deep inside your pretty mind</l>
          <l>It hits you.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>With so much pain</l>
          <l>Will you explain</l>
          <l>Please do!</l>
          <l>How do you make a dream come true?</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
